    "These associated works are summarised in detail in Table 10.",
    "One of the earliest studies found to automate the data extraction stage is by Kiritchenko et al. (2010).",
    "The study's primary purpose was to extract PICO elements and other pertinent information, such as DOI, publication date, funding number, and early stopping of trials, from full texts of RCTs.",
    "SVM was proposed to highlight necessary sentences from HTML files with a high probability of containing targeted information.",
